title: ***2 BR REMODELED APARTMENT @ Westbrooke Condos In Hopkins***
posting_body: ['When Convenience and Location is a Must!', 'Located conveniently to downtown Hopkins with dining, shopping, schools, entertainment, freeway access, and much more!', 'Minutes away from Shady Oak Beach Community, 18 parks and nature trails, and Hopkins Center for the Arts.', 'This apartment home will be REMODELED with new cabinets, new counter tops and new gleaming vinyl wood flooring, stainless steel appliances, new carpet and much more!', '(***DISCLOSURE: Photos may not be the exact design because we have a few different styles for the updates).', 'Call today and let our professional staff give you a personal tour of the community!', 'Lease Terms: Month-to-Month rental agreement with a 9 month clause', '$40 application fee per adult', '$400 Deposit', 'Cats accepted with the following restrictions: $200 non-refundable pet fee, $15 monthly pet rent, a limit of 2 cats per unit, and must be spayed/neutered', 'Utilities: Heat, Water, trash & sewage is paid by management, The resident is responsible for Electricity, Cable and internet.', '*Prices and availability are subject to change at any time.']
